    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This AP2-generation S2000 is a quintessential driver\u2019s machine, powered by the longitudinal F22C1 inline-four featuring Honda\u2019s iconic VTEC variable valve timing and an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise, short-throw six-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, providing exceptional corner-exit traction. Its rigid X-bone monocoque chassis and four-wheel double-wishbone suspension deliver communicative handling and neutral balance. This example has been meticulously serviced, showing strong compression and a responsive throttle. It remains in solid mechanical shape with a clean undercarriage, ready for spirited B-road driving.",
