      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily practicality. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014a testament to its enjoyed miles on the open road. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every button, dial, and digital interface functions exactly as intended, and the dual-zone climate control remains ice-cold even in peak summer. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent full synthetic oil change and a fresh set of performance tires installed just last season. The engine pulls smoothly across the rev range, and the transmission shifts with crisp precision, offering a confident and quiet ride. This is a turn-key vehicle, ready for its next owner to drive home with total peace of mind. Sale includes two sets of keys and a complete folder of documented service receipts.",
